ibe to the blog can see it. But still, it feels wrong, because it's not even like browser's \"reader mode\" — the user does not visit the original page at all.\r\n\r\nNot ok because:\r\n- Authors who only include a short summary in the RSS do so precisely because they want readers to visit their website. \r\n- Visiting the original blog is a much more personal experience than reading all blogs from the same UI of the reader app; bloggers craft their digital gardens for visitors!\r\n- Some blogs include styles, math, scripts, etc. which aren't rendered correctly elsewhere after scraping.\r\n\r\nOk because:\r\n- It's a nicer UX for the reader? \r\n\r\nCurious what others think.","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/6bca9e/is_it_ok_ethical_scrape_display_full_page","submitter_user":"freetonik","user_is_author":true,"tags":["ask","privacy"]},{"short_id":"qihnpz","short_id_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/qihnpz","created_at":"2024-10-25T23:43:37.000-05:00","title":"Improving SSH's security with SSHFP DNS records (2022)","url":"https://blog.apnic.net/2022/12/02/improving-sshs-security-with-sshfp-dns-records/","score":5,"flags":0,"comment_count":2,"description":"","description_plain":"","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/qihnpz/improving_ssh_s_security_with_sshfp_dns","submitter_user":"indigo","user_is_author":false,"tags":["cryptography"]},{"short_id":"zh4h99","short_id_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/zh4h99","created_at":"2024-10-25T09:15:53.000-05:00","title":"Generators with UnpinCell","url":"https://without.boats/blog/generators-with-unpin-cell/","score":15,"flags":0,"comment_count":3,"description":"","description_plain":"","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/zh4h99/generators_with_unpincell","submitter_user":"withoutboats","user_is_author":true,"tags":["rust"]},{"short_id":"torty9","short_id_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/torty9","created_at":"2024-10-26T05:30:00.000-05:00","title":"NimConf 2024 - online Nim conference","url":"https://conf.nim-lang.org","score":3,"flags":0,"comment_c